CHANGES FROM VERSION 2.14.6

* Added a switch (for debugging purposes) to make 'merge' commands retain temporary
  files after they are finished

-------------------------------
CHANGES FROM VERSION 2.14.0

* Incorporated Ben Willmore's cool new icon for the Mac UI.
* Fixed off by one error in month numbers (in printed dates) reported 
  by Bob Burger
* append just the major version number (2.13), not the full version
  (2.13.15) when constructing the remote server command name in the
  presence of -addversionno preference.  (Thanks to Karl M for the
  suggestion.)
* Fixed (I hope!) export procedure so that "Changes in..." message in embedded 
  documentation has the correct version number.
-------------------------------
CHANGES FROM VERSION 2.14.-13

Complete reimplementation of backup functionality by Stephane Lescuyer
(thanks, Stephane!)  See the manual (in particular, the description of
the backup... preferences) for details.

NOT YET THOROUGHLY TESTED!  Use with caution...


    
